hopobject.body: How many weeks' holiday a year are there? healthmeddoc.com I’m still waiting for Ojomo and Tracy to impress me. Tracy got on the field vs starters and was invisible to me. Ojomo continues to embarrass car salesmen and future MMA rejects but hasn’t stepped on the field vs anything resembling NFL talent. He’s put up some nice numbers but the coaches still refuse to let him see early playing time and that speaks volumes to me. Maybe that will change in the coming weeks but for right now, meh.
